<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5224089>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Rostrocalanus peracutus sp. nov. Female, holotype. (A) Habitus, dorsal; (B) habitus, lateral; (C) cephalosome, lateral; (D) rostrum, ventral; (E) posterior prosome and urosome, right lateral; (F) posterior prosome and urosome, dorsal; (G) anal somite and caudal rami, dorsal; (H) antennule I–XI segments; (J) antennule, segments XII–XX; (K) antennule, segments XXI–XXVIII. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5224089/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5224091>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Rostrocalanus peracutus sp. nov. Female. (A) Antenna; (B) mandible; (C) mandible, exopod; (D, E) mandible, gnathobase; (F) maxillule; (G) maxillule, praecoxal arthrite; (H) maxilla; (J) maxilla, sensory seta of endopod. (A–F, H, J) Holotype, (G) paratype. Scale bars: (E) 0.05 mm, (A–D, F–J) 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5224091/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5224093>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Rostrocalanus peracutus sp. nov. Female, holotype. (A) Maxilliped, endopod; arrow indicates damage; (B) maxilliped; (C) P1; (D) P2; (E) P3; (F) P4; (G) P5, anterior. Scale bars: (A) 0.05 mm, (B–G) 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5224093/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

